          Transform your entrepeneurial journey with a structured approach to
          productivity, energy management, and personal growth
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <!-- icon -->
          <div></div>

          <h3>Mission</h3>

          <p>
            Set clear goals an focus on what matters most. Define your daily
            mission with precision
          </p>

          <ul role="list">
            <li><span class="check-icon">&check;</span> Daily goal setting</li>
            <li><span class="check-icon">&check;</span> Daily goal setting</li>
            <li><span class="check-icon">&check;</span> Daily goal setting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>


        <div class="card">
          <!-- icon -->
          <div></div>

          <h3>Mission</h3>

          <p>
            Set clear goals an focus on what matters most. Define your daily
            mission with precision
          </p>

          <ul role="list">
            <li><span class="check-icon">&check;</span> Daily goal setting</li>
            <li><span class="check-icon">&check;</span> Daily goal setting</li>
            <li><span class="check-icon">&check;</span> Daily goal setting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <!-- icon -->
          <div></div>

          <h3>Mission</h3>

          <p>
            Set clear goals an focus on what matters most. Define your daily
            mission with precision
          </p>

          <ul role="list">
            <li><span class="check-icon">&check;</span> Daily goal setting</li>
            <li><span class="check-icon">&check;</span> Daily goal setting</li>
            <li><span class="check-icon">&check;</span> Daily goal setting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  #pilars-section {
    background-color: var(--clr-neutral-100);

    .section-wrapper {
      display: grid;
      gap: var(--space-lg);

      .section-title {
        text-align: center;
        margin-inline: auto;
        max-width: 65ch;

        h2 {
          margin-block-end: var(--space-sm);
        }
      }


      .card-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: var(--space-sm);
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(15rem, 1fr));

        .card {
          background-color: var(--clr-neutral-50);
          border-radius: var(--radius-md);
          box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
          display: grid;
          gap: var(--space-sm);
          padding: var(--space-md);
          transition: var(--transition-medium);

          div {
            width: 3rem;
            height: 3rem;
            background-color: var(--clr-accent-gold);
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
          }

          .check-icon {
            color: var(--clr-accent-gold);
            font-weight: var(--fw-bold);
          }

          ul {
            display: grid;
            gap: var(--space-sm);
          }

          &:hover,
          &:focus {
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            transform: translateY(-10px);
          }

        }
      }
    }
  }
</style>
